## Input

```css
.test {
  color: if(style(--scheme: dark): #eeeeee; else: black;);
  background: if(media(print): white; else: black;);
  border-color: if(supports(color: red): red; else: blue;);
  outline-color: if(not style(--scheme: light): white; else: black;);
  accent-color: if((style(--scheme: dark)): green; else: red;);
  height: if(is-valid-size($size), $size, 100px);
	inline-size: if(sass($size > 10px): 12px;else: 10px;);
}

```


